      <title>对冲基金在特朗普关税之后以创纪录的速度扭转了石油赌注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/hedge-funds-reversed-oil-bets-at-record-pace-after-trump-tariffs</link>
